        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 4: Immunostaining of primary striatal rat neurons, infected with Flag-Slitrk5 lentivirus and transfected with PSD95 fused to mCherry, showed co-localization of Slitrk5 and PSD95 (DLG4) in synaptic puncta. Resolution of imaging was too low to further elucidate subcellular localization.. Experimental description: M&M: \"Figure 4: Immunostaining of primary striatal rat neurons\"" ;
